<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>David Reina — Engineering Portfolio</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0a;
    --surface: #111111;
    --surface2: #181818;
    --border: #222222;
    --accent: #e8d5a3;
    --accent2: #c4a882;
    --accent-glow: rgba(232,213,163,0.12);
    --text: #f0ece4;
    --text-dim: #7a7570;
    --text-mid: #b0aa9f;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-x: hidden; cursor: none; }
  #cursor { position: fixed; width: 10px; height: 10px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); transition: width 0.2s, height 0.2s; mix-blend-mode: difference; }
  #cursor.expand { width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(232,213,163,0.3); }
  nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 20px 48px; background: rgba(10,10,10,0.88); backdrop-filter: blur(16px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .nav-logo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; cursor: none; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--text-dim); text-decoration: none; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; cursor: none; }
  .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: var(--accent); }
  .page { display: none; min-height: 100vh; padding-top: 72px; }
  .page.active { display: block; }
  /* COVER */
  #page-cover { display: none; position: relative; min-height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  #page-cover.active { display: flex; }
  .cover-grid { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(232,213,163,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232,213,163,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px; }
  .cover-orb { position: absolute; width: 600px; height: 600px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,213,163,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%); border-radius: 50%; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); animation: orb-pulse 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes orb-pulse { 0%,100% { transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1); opacity:.6; } 50% { transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.15); opacity:1; } }
  .cover-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; text-align: center; max-width: 900px; padding: 0 48px; }
  .cover-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 32px; opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.2s forwards; }
  .cover-name { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 120px); line-height: 0.95; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 24px; opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.4s forwards; }
  .cover-name span { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; }
  .cover-subtitle { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 22px; color: var(--text-mid); margin-bottom: 48px; opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.6s forwards; }
  .cover-divider { width: 1px; height: 60px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), transparent); margin: 0 auto 48px; opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.8s forwards; }
  .cover-tagline { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 56px; opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 1s forwards; }
  .cover-cta { display: inline-flex; gap: 16px; opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 1.2s forwards; }
  .btn { padding: 12px 28px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; border: none; cursor: none; transition: all 0.25s; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--text); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .corner-deco { position: absolute; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 0.1em; opacity: 0.5; line-height: 1.6; }
  .corner-deco.tl { top: 90px; left: 48px; }
  .corner-deco.tr { top: 90px; right: 48px; text-align: right; }
  .corner-deco.bl { bottom: 40px; left: 48px; }
  .corner-deco.br { bottom: 40px; right: 48px; text-align: right; }
  .cover-scroll { position: absolute; bottom: 40px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 1s 1.6s forwards; }
  .scroll-line { width: 1px; height: 40px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--text-dim), transparent); animation: sl 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes sl { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scaleY(1)} 50%{opacity:.3;transform:scaleY(.5)} }
  @keyframes fade-up { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
  /* PAGES */
  .page-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 48px; }
  .section-tag { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(36px,6vw,72px); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .italic-accent { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  /* ABOUT */
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 72px; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 72px; }
  .portrait-box { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .portrait-box::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(232,213,163,.03) 0%,transparent 60%); }
  .pc { position: absolute; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-color: var(--accent); border-style: solid; border-width: 0; opacity: 0.6; }
  .pc.tl{top:-1px;left:-1px;border-top-width:2px;border-left-width:2px}
  .pc.tr{top:-1px;right:-1px;border-top-width:2px;border-right-width:2px}
  .pc.bl{bottom:-1px;left:-1px;border-bottom-width:2px;border-left-width:2px}
  .pc.br{bottom:-1px;right:-1px;border-bottom-width:2px;border-right-width:2px}
  .flag-chip { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-mid); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .lead { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 20px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .about-bio p { color: var(--text-mid); margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.9; }
  .about-bio strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 400; }
  .stats-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .stat-item { background: var(--bg); padding: 28px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 36px; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .skills-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 48px; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .skill-cat h3 { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .skill-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(34,34,34,.5); font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .sbar { width: 80px; height: 2px; background: var(--border); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .sbar-fill { position: absolute; left:0; top:0; height:100%; background: var(--accent); transform-origin:left; animation: bfill 1.5s ease-out forwards; }
  @keyframes bfill { from{transform:scaleX(0)} to{transform:scaleX(1)} }
  .edu-block { border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px; position: relative; background: var(--surface); }
  .edu-block::before { content:'EDUCATION'; position:absolute; top:-6px; left:24px; background:var(--surface); padding:0 8px; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:.3em; color:var(--accent); text-transform:uppercase; }
  .edu-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .edu-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .edu-school { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); }
  .edu-detail { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .edu-year { font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent); white-space: nowrap; }
  /* PROJECTS */
  #page-projects .page-inner { max-width: 1200px; }
  .proj-intro { max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .proj-intro p { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; line-height: 1.9; }
  .proj-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .pcard { background: var(--bg); padding: 36px 28px; cursor: none; transition: background .25s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .pcard::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent-glow),transparent); opacity:0; transition:opacity .3s; }
  .pcard:hover { background: var(--surface); }
  .pcard:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .pcard:hover .pnum { color: var(--accent); opacity: .3; }
  .pnum { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--border); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 20px; transition: color .3s; }
  .ptag { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .ptitle { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.3; }
  .pdesc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .plink { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: gap .2s; cursor: none; }
  .plink:hover { gap: 14px; }
  .plink::after { content: '→'; }
  .pcard.featured { grid-column: span 2; background: var(--surface); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); }
  .pcard.featured .ptitle { font-size: 22px; }
  /* DETAIL */
  #page-project-detail { padding: 100px 0 80px; }
  .det-hero { padding: 80px 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative; overflow: hidden; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .det-hero::after { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; right:0; width:40%; height:100%; background:linear-gradient(to left,var(--accent-glow),transparent); pointer-events:none; }
  .back-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); cursor: none; transition: color .2s; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .back-link::before { content: '←'; }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .det-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .det-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(28px,4.5vw,58px); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.02em; max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .det-sub { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-mid); max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .meta-row { display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .mi { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .ml { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .mv { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); }
  .dbody { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 72px 48px; }
  .dbody h2 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--text); margin: 56px 0 20px; padding-top: 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .dbody h2::before { content: attr(data-n); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .15em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 400; }
  .dbody p { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 13px; line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .dbody strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 400; }
  .dbody ul { list-style: none; margin: 16px 0 24px; }
  .dbody ul li { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 12px; padding: 6px 0 6px 20px; position: relative; line-height: 1.8; }
  .dbody ul li::before { content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--accent); }
  .callout { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding: 24px 28px; margin: 32px 0; background: var(--surface); }
  .callout p { color: var(--text); font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }
  .scard { border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 24px; margin: 12px 0; background: var(--surface); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr; gap: 20px; align-items: start; transition: border-color .2s; }
  .scard:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .sbadge { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 30px; color: var(--accent); opacity: .5; line-height: 1; }
  .stitle { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .sdesc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.8; }
  .tline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; margin: 24px 0; }
  .tline::before { content:''; position:absolute; left:0; top:0; bottom:0; width:1px; background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--accent),var(--border)); }
  .titem { position: relative; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .titem::before { content:''; position:absolute; left:-36px; top:6px; width:8px; height:8px; border:1px solid var(--accent); background:var(--bg); transform:rotate(45deg); }
  .tphase { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .ttext { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.8; }
  .spec-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; font-size: 12px; }
  .spec-table th { text-align: left; padding: 10px 16px; background: var(--surface2); color: var(--accent); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 400; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .spec-table td { padding: 10px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-mid); }
  .spec-table tr:hover td { background: var(--surface); color: var(--text); }
  .refs { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 48px; margin-top: 48px; }
  .refs h3 { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .ref { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(34,34,34,.5); line-height: 1.7; }
  .det-footer { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:48px; padding-top:32px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); }
  .det-footer-left { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .det-footer-left span { display: block; color: var(--text-mid); margin-top: 4px; }
  footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px 48px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 11px; }
  ::selection { background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px} ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg)} ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border)} ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover{background:var(--accent)}
  @media(max-width:768px){
    nav{padding:16px 24px}
    .page-inner{padding:60px 24px}
    .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
    .stats-row{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
    .skills-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .proj-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .pcard.featured{grid-column:span 1}
    .det-hero{padding:60px 24px}
    .dbody{padding:48px 24px}
    footer{flex-direction:column;gap:12px;text-align:center}
    .cover-name{font-size:48px}
    .corner-deco{display:none}
    .nav-links{gap:16px}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="cursor"></div>

<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#" onclick="showPage('cover');return false;">DR</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('cover');return false;" id="nav-cover" class="active">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('about');return false;" id="nav-about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('projects');return false;" id="nav-projects">Projects</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- COVER -->
<div id="page-cover" class="page active">
  <div class="cover-grid"></div>
  <div class="cover-orb"></div>
  <div class="cover-content">
    <div class="cover-eyebrow">Engineering Portfolio · 2026</div>
    <h1 class="cover-name">David<br><span>Reina</span></h1>
    <p class="cover-subtitle">Aerospace &amp; Systems Engineering</p>
    <div class="cover-divider"></div>
    <p class="cover-tagline">From Honduras to Mars — designing the systems that get us there.</p>
    <div class="cover-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#" onclick="showPage('projects');return false;">View Projects</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline" href="#" onclick="showPage('about');return false;">About Me</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="corner-deco tl">Walt Whitman High School<br>Bethesda, MD</div>
  <div class="corner-deco tr">Rice Aerospace Academy<br>Summer 2025</div>
  <div class="corner-deco bl">v1.0 · 2026</div>
  <div class="corner-deco br">Honduras 🇭🇳</div>
  <div class="cover-scroll"><div class="scroll-line"></div>Explore</div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<div id="page-about" class="page">
  <div class="page-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">01 — About</div>
    <h1 class="section-title">The Engineer<br><span class="italic-accent">Behind the Work</span></h1>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="portrait-box">
          <div class="pc tl"></div><div class="pc tr"></div><div class="pc bl"></div><div class="pc br"></div>
          <div style="font-size:48px;opacity:.15">◎</div>
          <div style="text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.2em;font-size:11px">Photo coming soon</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-bio">
        <div class="flag-chip">🇭🇳 Honduras &nbsp;·&nbsp; Bethesda, MD</div>
        <p class="lead">"I build things that haven't been built yet — from prosthetic hands to spacecraft that return from Mars."</p>
        <p>My name is <strong>David Reina</strong>, a student at <strong>Walt Whitman High School</strong> in Bethesda, Maryland. Originally from <strong>Honduras</strong>, I carry a perspective shaped by two worlds — and a drive to engineer solutions that matter across both of them.</p>
        <p>In the summer of 2025 I attended the <strong>Rice Aerospace Academy (Envision by WorldStrides)</strong> at Rice University, where my team designed a conceptual <strong>5-stage Mars Sample Return Lander</strong> — one of the most ambitious challenges in modern space exploration.</p>
        <p>My work spans 3D modeling and printing, CAD design, mission architecture, propulsion analysis, and hands-on fabrication with materials like balsa wood and prosthetic components. I've also competed internationally — representing Honduras at a <strong>Shanghai sustainable city design camp</strong> with students from 10+ countries.</p>
        <p>I approach every project by grounding ideas in real physics and real constraints — budget, materials, and time — then iterating until the design actually works. That discipline, and a deep curiosity about how things fly, drives everything I build.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">5</div><div class="stat-label">Projects</div></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">10+</div><div class="stat-label">Countries Collaborated</div></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">2025</div><div class="stat-label">Rice Aerospace Academy</div></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">🇭🇳</div><div class="stat-label">Honduras</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-cat">
        <h3>Engineering Tools</h3>
        <div class="skill-row">Onshape / GrabCAD <div class="sbar"><div class="sbar-fill" style="width:85%"></div></div></div>
        <div class="skill-row">3D Printing <div class="sbar"><div class="sbar-fill" style="width:80%"></div></div></div>
        <div class="skill-row">Plane Maker / Sim <div class="sbar"><div class="sbar-fill" style="width:70%"></div></div></div>
        <div class="skill-row">Technical Sketching <div class="sbar"><div class="sbar-fill" style="width:90%"></div></div></div>
      </div>
