  <h1 class="det-title">Water Pressure Rocket &amp; Budget Lab</h1>
  <p class="det-sub">A design-and-build competition where budget constraints were as much the engineering challenge as aerodynamics — building under economic pressure.</p>
  <div class="meta-row">
    <div class="mi"><span class="ml">Program</span><span class="mv">Rice Aerospace Academy</span></div>
    <div class="mi"><span class="ml">Type</span><span class="mv">Lab / Competition</span></div>
    <div class="mi"><span class="ml">Focus</span><span class="mv">Budget Engineering · Aerospace</span></div>
